heck-nicola-valley-institute-of-technology-application-portal-how-to-check-nvit-application-status\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Check_Nicola_Valley_Institute_of_Technology_Application_Portal_How_to_Check_NVIT_Application_Status\"><\/span><strong>How to Check Nicola Valley Institute of Technology Application Portal | How to Check NVIT Application Status<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>To view the status of your application, including outstanding necessities, please kindly login in to the University online application system to view your admission application status.<\/p>\n<p>Click <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.nvit.ca\/mynvitlogoemployees.htm\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a><\/strong> to view University\u2019s Admission Application Status<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-accept-the-offer-and-pay-the-admission-deposit-how-to-check-nicola-valley-institute-of-technology-application-status\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_accept_the_offer_and_pay_the_Admission_Deposit_How_to_check_Nicola_Valley_Institute_of_Technology_Application_Status\"><\/span><strong>How to accept the offer and pay the Admission Deposit? | How to check Nicola Valley Institute of Technology Application Status<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Using <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.nvit.ca\/internationalstudents.htm\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/www.nvit.ca<\/a><\/strong>. To accept your offer of admission and pay the affirmation deposit where relevant.<\/li>\n<li>click <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/nvit-tuition-2024\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a><\/strong> to see fees directives for payment<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>The next step is to enroll online; an exact date will be issued to you by the university.<\/p>\n<p>Your account will help you track all things you need to know before and after being admitted.<\/p>\n<p><strong><em>And now you know how to check your application status by checking your student\u2019s account we hope this information was helpful kindly drop your comment in the comment box as we look toward your expectations.<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>See also&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<a title=\"British Council Scholarship Award, IELTS Award\" href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/british-council-scholarship-award\/\" rel=\"bookmark nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">British Council Scholarship Award, IELTS Award<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n<div class=\"group w-full text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 border-b border-black\/10 dark:border-gray-900\/50 dark:bg-gray-800\">\n<div class=\"text-base gap-4 md:gap-6 md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-xl xl:max-w-3xl p-4 md:py-6 flex lg:px-0 m-auto\">\n<div class=\"relative flex w-[calc(100%-50px)] flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3 lg:w-[calc(100%-115px)]\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-grow flex-col gap-3\">\n<h2 id=\"nvit-application-portal-login\" class=\"min-h-[20px] flex flex-col items-start gap-4 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"NVIT_Application_Portal_login\"><\/span><strong>NVIT Application Portal login<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"flex justify-between lg:block\">To access your NVIT Application Status login, please follow these steps:<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"group w-full text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 border-b border-black\/10 dark:border-gray-900\/50 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-[#444654]\">\n<div class=\"text-base gap-4 md:gap-6 md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-xl xl:max-w-3xl p-4 md:py-6 flex lg:px-0 m-auto\">\n<div class=\"relative flex w-[calc(100%-50px)] flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3 lg:w-[calc(100%-115px)]\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-grow flex-col gap-3\">\n<div class=\"min-h-[20px] flex flex-col items-start gap-4 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words\">\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light\">\n<ol>\n<li>Go to the Nicola Valley Institute of Technology&#8217;s <a href=\"https:\/\/www.nvit.ca\/current-students\/student-information-system.htm\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">website<\/a>.<\/li>\n<li>Click on the &#8220;Student Information System&#8221; link.<\/li>\n<li>You will be redirected to a login page.<\/li>\n<li>Enter your username and password.<\/li>\n<li>Once logged in, you should be able to view your application status.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"How to Check NVIT Application Status, How to accept the Offer and pay for the Admission Deposit, Tuition&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":12977,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[448],"tags":[755],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2575"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2575"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2575\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/12977"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2575"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2575"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2575"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}